Rating: 4
A+++. I can't wait to make this again - for company next time! Easy and elegant. Carrots gave lots of color served alongside wilted spinach. I sauteed the scallops in butter instead of olive oil. I omitted tomatoes and cilantro and increased the carrots. Next time I would add maybe zuchini or another subtle vegetable that would give the dish more body but not overpower the scallops. The balsamic vinegar I used was almost too much for the scallops but came off fine.

